	   <tr><td colspan=2>1 point overlooked a lot when discussing race/ stats on war is the Ogres being immune to stun from frontal attack. In my opinion this is an overwhelming advantage and is not something that can be made up through equipment. Consider the number of attacks you miss when you are stunned. Consider the amount of agro you can build with those attacks. Attacks that other races would not be making because they are stunned.&nbsp;&nbsp;Combine this with the nice starting stats and Ogre is very hard to beat.<br><br>I still agree that you should play whatever race appeals to you, because you will probably play the character more, level faster, and have more fun...but consider Ogre strongly before making warrior.<br>&nbsp;<br>Frostpaw<br>Barbarian Warrior<br>51 seasons<br>Cazic Thule Server</td></tr>
